#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks home page"
msgstr "Järjehoidjate kodulehekülg"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "This module lets you configure the bookmarks home page."
msgstr "See moodul võimaldab seadistada järjehoidjate kodulehekülge."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view the bookmarks home page enter <userinput>bookmarks:/</userinput> in "
"the location bar."
msgstr ""
"Järjehoidjate kodulehekülje nägemiseks sisesta asukoharibale "
"<userinput>bookmarks:/</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The settings in this module are also accessible by entering "
"<userinput>bookmarks:/config</userinput> in the location bar."
msgstr ""
"Seda moodulit saab seadistada ka siis, kui sisestada asukoharibale "
"<userinput>bookmarks:/config</userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "General settings"
msgstr "Üldised seadistused"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of columns to show"
msgstr "Näidatavate veergude arv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Folders are automatically distributed in several columns. The optimal "
#| "number of columns depends on the width of the konqueror window and the "
#| "number of bookmarks you have."
msgid ""
"Folders are automatically distributed in several columns. The optimal number "
"of columns depends on the width of the &konqueror; window and the number of "
"bookmarks you have."
msgstr ""
"Kataloogid jagatakse automaatselt mitmesse veergu. Veergude optimaalne arv "
"sõltub Konquerori akna laiusest ja sinu järjehoidjate arvust."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show folder backgrounds"
msgstr "Kataloogide tausta näitamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disable it on slow system to disable background images."
msgstr "Aeglase süsteemi korral on mõttekas taustapildid välja lülitada."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show bookmarks without folder"
msgstr "Kataloogita järjehoidjate näitamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If this option is unchecked, bookmarks at the root of the hierarchy (not "
#| "in a folder) are not displayed. If checked, they are gathered in a \"root"
#| "\" folder."
msgid ""
"If this option is unchecked, bookmarks at the root of the hierarchy (not in "
"a folder) are not displayed. If checked, they are gathered in a “root” "
"folder."
msgstr ""
"Selle valimata jätmisel ei näidata hierarhia juurkataloogis olevaid "
"järjehoidjaid. Kui see on valitud, koondatakse nad kataloogi \"juur\"."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Flatten bookmarks tree"
msgstr "Ühtlane järjehoidjapuu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sub-folders are shown within their parent by default. If you activate this "
"option, sub-folders are displayed on their own. It looks less nice but it "
"may help if you have a very big folder you want to spread in two columns."
msgstr ""
"Vaikimisi näidatakse alamkatalooge nende eellase all. Selle valiku "
"sisselülitamisel näidatakse alamkatalooge omaette. See ei ole vahest nii "
"kena, aga võib olla abiks, kui sul on väga suur kataloog ja sa soovid seda "
"näha kahes veerus."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show system places"
msgstr "Süsteemi asukohtade näitamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Show a box with KDE places (Home, Network, ...). Useful if you use "
#| "konqueror as a file manager."
msgid ""
"Show a box with common places (Home, Network, …). Useful if you use "
"&konqueror; as a file manager."
msgstr ""
"Kasti näitamine KDE asukohtadega (Kodu, Võrk...). See on abiks, kui kasutada "
"failihaldurina Konquerori."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pixmap cache"
msgstr "Pildipuhver"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disk cache size"
msgstr "Kettapuhvri suurus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify how much disk space is used to cache the pixmaps."
msgstr "Määrab, kui palju kettaruumi eraldada piltide puhverdamiseks."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clear Cache"
msgstr "Tühjenda puhver"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Remove all cached images. This may be necessary if some favicons become "
#| "corrupt and don't refresh automatically."
msgid ""
"Remove all cached images. This may be necessary if some favicons become "
"corrupt and don’t refresh automatically."
msgstr ""
"Eemaldab kõik puhverdatud pildid. See võib olla vajalik, kui mõned "
"lemmikikoonid riknevad ega värskenda end enam automaatselt."

